title: EC observer should write logs under ~/.clawq
---

The self-correction / Error Correction observer does not appear to emit its runtime logs into daemon.log. It does not need to log there specifically, but it should write observable logs somewhere under ~/.clawq so failures, loops, and decisions can be inspected after the fact.
